---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Revenue CRM (Beta) | The AI-native CRM that follows your revenue model"
	description="Unify sales, marketing, and CS revenue data in one place. Revenue CRM scores leads and suggests the next action with AI. Now in closed beta. Request a demo."
	lang="en"
	alternateUrl="/crm/"
	noindex={true}
>

<!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
<section class="hero">
	<div class="container">
		<span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>Product · Closed Beta</span>
		<h1>The AI-native CRM that<br />follows your revenue model.</h1>
		<p class="hero-lead">
			Capture leads, run deals, and forecast — all in one place. AI scores prospects
			and recommends the next action, keeping your sales, marketing, and CS revenue
			operations moving forward. Now available to a small number of companies in closed beta.
		</p>
		<div class="hero-actions">
			<a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn--hero-primary btn--lg">Request a demo →</a>
			<a href="#features" class="btn btn--hero-outline btn--lg">See features</a>
		</div>
		<p class="hero-note">* Currently in beta — invite-only and limited to a few companies. Features may change without notice.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== DEMO VIDEO ===================== -->
<section class="demo-video">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="video-frame">
			<video
				src="/videos/revenue-crm.mp4"
				controls
				preload="metadata"
				playsinline
				width="1280"
				height="720"
			></video>
		</div>
		<p class="video-caption">Product demo (about 2 min 40 sec)</p>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== PROBLEM ===================== -->
<section class="problem">
	<div class="container">
		<p class="section-eyebrow">Why CRM fails</p>
		<h2 class="prob-title">Sound familiar?</h2>
		<div class="prob-grid">
			<div class="prob-item">
				<p>Data entry is a chore, so the team never adopts it — and you quietly drift back to managing everything in Excel.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="prob-item">
				<p>SFA, MA, and CS tools are siloed, so the numbers from lead to revenue never connect into one view.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="prob-item">
				<p>Which lead to act on now, and what to do next, lives in people's heads — so follow-up is always reactive.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== FEATURES ===================== -->
<section class="features" id="features">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="feat-head">
			<p class="section-eyebrow">Features</p>
			<h2>Built to move revenue forward.</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="feat-grid">
			<article class="feat-card">
				<h3>AI agent</h3>
				<p>Ask your data in plain language. AI drafts emails and recommends next steps, taking work off the team's plate.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="feat-card">
				<h3>Lead scoring</h3>
				<p>Surface hot leads automatically from behavior and firmographics. See who to act on at a glance.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="feat-card">
				<h3>Workflow automation</h3>
				<p>Trigger notifications, tasks, and emails on your rules — cut manual work and prevent things from slipping.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="feat-card">
				<h3>Email sequences</h3>
				<p>Automated, multi-step follow-ups that branch based on each reply and action.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="feat-card">
				<h3>Forecasting</h3>
				<p>See where the quarter lands straight from your pipeline — turn meetings into decisions, not status reports.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="feat-card">
				<h3>Custom objects</h3>
				<p>Extend the data model to fit your business. Design it around how revenue actually flows.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== ALL FEATURES ===================== -->
<section class="all-features">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="feat-head">
			<p class="section-eyebrow">All features</p>
			<h2>Sales, marketing, CS, and ops — in one place.</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="cat-grid">
			<div class="cat-card">
				<h3>AI &amp; Intelligence</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>AI Copilot (search &amp; operate the CRM in plain language)</li>
					<li>AI call analysis (MEDDPICC / BANT / CHAMP / SPIN)</li>
					<li>AI research (web, with citations)</li>
					<li>AI summarization &amp; classification</li>
					<li>AI attribute fields (AI columns on records)</li>
					<li>Voice transcription (Whisper)</li>
					<li>Lead scoring (grades A–F)</li>
					<li>Workspace credit management</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="cat-card">
				<h3>CRM core</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Contacts / Companies / Deals</li>
					<li>Tickets / Tasks / Activities / Calls</li>
					<li>Deal kanban (drag &amp; drop)</li>
					<li>Lead conversion (stage change + deal)</li>
					<li>Pipeline &amp; stage management</li>
					<li>Notes, attachments &amp; favorites</li>
					<li>Record-to-record relations</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="cat-card">
				<h3>Marketing</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Form builder (public pages, auto-create contacts)</li>
					<li>Email campaigns &amp; templates</li>
					<li>Open / click tracking &amp; unsubscribe</li>
					<li>Lists (static / dynamic)</li>
					<li>Workflows (visual automation)</li>
					<li>Triggers, conditions &amp; delays</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="cat-card">
				<h3>Sales</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Forecasting (by category)</li>
					<li>Sequences (automated follow-up)</li>
					<li>Quotes (line items, tax, status)</li>
					<li>Product catalog</li>
					<li>Contact roles (decision maker, champion, …)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="cat-card">
				<h3>Customer Success</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Omnichannel inbox (chat / email / API)</li>
					<li>Embeddable chat widget (real-time)</li>
					<li>Inbound email to conversations</li>
					<li>Knowledge base</li>
					<li>Surveys (NPS / CSAT / CES)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="cat-card">
				<h3>Platform &amp; extensibility</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Custom objects &amp; custom fields</li>
					<li>Record types &amp; relationship definitions</li>
					<li>REST API (v1) / GraphQL / MCP server</li>
					<li>Outbound webhooks (signed, with delivery logs)</li>
					<li>Permissions (role × CRUD) &amp; audit log</li>
					<li>Multi-workspace, member invites &amp; roles</li>
					<li>Trash (restore) &amp; global search</li>
					<li>Notion / Google / LinkedIn integrations</li>
					<li>Multilingual (JA / EN / ZH-TW)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== BETA NOTE ===================== -->
<section class="beta-band">
	<div class="container beta-inner">
		<div>
			<p class="section-eyebrow">Closed Beta</p>
			<h2>We're onboarding our first customers now.</h2>
			<p class="beta-lead">
				Revenue CRM is being built in closed beta. Beta customers get onboarding
				informed by Consilegy's revenue-design expertise, plus priority support
				where your feature requests go straight into the product.
			</p>
		</div>
		<ul class="beta-list">
			<li>Hands-on setup and data migration support</li>
			<li>Advice on revenue operations design</li>
			<li>Priority on your feature requests</li>
			<li>Preferential terms during the beta</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== FINAL CTA ===================== -->
<section class="final-cta">
	<div class="container cta-inner">
		<div>
			<p class="cta-eyebrow">Get Started</p>
			<h2>See it in action<br />with a live demo.</h2>
			<p class="cta-lead">
				We'll walk through your revenue operations challenges and show how
				Revenue CRM works in a hands-on demo. Beta inquiries are welcome here too.
			</p>
			<div class="cta-actions">
				<a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn--cta-primary btn--lg">Request a demo →</a>
				<a href="/en/services/" class="btn btn--cta-outline btn--lg">View services</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="cta-card">
			<h4>What we'll show you</h4>
			<ul class="cta-list">
				<li>AI agent operating on and suggesting actions from your data</li>
				<li>Lead scoring and prioritization</li>
				<li>Workflow and email-sequence automation</li>
				<li>Pipeline and forecast visibility</li>
				<li>Customization examples for your operations</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ── Shared ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
.section-eyebrow {
	font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary);
	letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
}
.btn--lg { padding: 1.0625rem 1.875rem; font-size: 1rem; }

/* ── Hero ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
	background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-bg-subtle) 0%, var(--color-bg) 100%);
	border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	padding-block: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
}
.eyebrow {
	display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
	font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary);
	background: rgba(30,64,175,0.08); padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem; border-radius: 4px;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.eyebrow__dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary); display: inline-block; }
.hero h1 {
	font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 600;
	letter-spacing: 0.01em; margin: 0 0 1rem; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.2;
}
.hero-lead { font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 720px; margin: 0 0 2rem; }
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero-note { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 1.5rem 0 0; }

.btn--hero-primary {
	display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
	background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff;
	padding: 1.0625rem 1.875rem; border-radius: var(--radius);
	font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; border: none;
	transition: background 0.15s ease;
}
.btn--hero-primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-dark); color: #fff; }
.btn--hero-outline {
	display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
	background: transparent; color: var(--color-primary);
	padding: 1.0625rem 1.875rem; border-radius: var(--radius);
	font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none;
	border: 1.5px solid var(--color-primary);
	transition: all 0.15s ease;
}
.btn--hero-outline:hover { background: rgba(30,64,175,0.06); }

/* ── Demo video ────────────────────────────────────── */
.demo-video { padding-block: var(--space-xl); background: var(--color-bg); }
.video-frame {
	max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto;
	border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-card);
	overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); background: #000;
	line-height: 0;
}
.video-frame video { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
.video-caption { text-align: center; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 1rem 0 0; }

/* ── Problem ───────────────────────────────────────── */
.problem { padding-block: var(--space-2xl); background: var(--color-bg); }
.prob-title { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 2rem; }
.prob-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
.prob-item {
	border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-card);
	padding: 1.75rem; background: var(--color-bg-subtle);
	border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
}
.prob-item p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text); }

/* ── Features ──────────────────────────────────────── */
.features { padding-block: var(--space-2xl); background: var(--color-bg-subtle); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.feat-head { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.feat-head h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }
.feat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
.feat-card {
	border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-card);
	padding: 1.75rem; background: var(--color-bg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}
.feat-card h3 { font-size: 1.0625rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 0.625rem; }
.feat-card p { font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; }

/* ── All features ──────────────────────────────────── */
.all-features { padding-block: var(--space-2xl); background: var(--color-bg); }
.cat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
.cat-card {
	border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-card);
	padding: 1.75rem; background: var(--color-bg-subtle);
}
.cat-card h3 {
	font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary);
	letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin: 0 0 1rem; padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
	border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.cat-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
.cat-card li {
	display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: flex-start;
	font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-text);
	padding: 0.3rem 0;
}
.cat-card li::before { content: "✓"; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 700; }

/* ── Beta band ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.beta-band { padding-block: var(--space-2xl); background: var(--color-bg); }
.beta-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; align-items: center; }
.beta-inner h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 1.9rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; }
.beta-lead { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; }
.beta-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
.beta-list li {
	display: flex; gap: 0.625rem; align-items: flex-start;
	padding: 0.625rem 0; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text);
	border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); line-height: 1.6;
}
.beta-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.beta-list li::before { content: "✓"; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 700; }

/* ── Final CTA ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.final-cta {
	background:
		radial-gradient(800px 360px at 85% -5%, rgba(124,92,191,0.35), transparent 55%),
		linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
	color: #fff; padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
}
.cta-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
.cta-eyebrow { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #93c5fd; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
.cta-inner h2 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 2.5vw, 2.25rem); line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
.cta-lead { color: #bfdbfe; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 2rem; }
.cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

.btn--cta-primary {
	display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
	padding: 1.0625rem 1.875rem; border-radius: var(--radius);
	font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none;
	background: #fff; color: var(--color-primary); border: none;
	transition: background 0.15s ease;
}
.btn--cta-primary:hover { background: #e0eaff; color: var(--color-primary); }
.btn--cta-outline {
	display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
	padding: 1.0625rem 1.875rem; border-radius: var(--radius);
	font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none;
	background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
	transition: all 0.15s ease;
}
.btn--cta-outline:hover { border-color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

.cta-card {
	background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
	border-radius: var(--radius-card); padding: 2rem; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}
.cta-card h4 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #93c5fd; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; }
.cta-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
.cta-list li {
	display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;
	padding: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #e0eaff;
	border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); line-height: 1.6;
}
.cta-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.cta-list li::before { content: ""; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 9px; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: #93c5fd; }

/* ── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 960px) {
	.prob-grid, .feat-grid, .cat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	.beta-inner, .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
}
@media (max-width: 560px) {
	.hero-actions, .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; }
}
</style>
